WEBVTT

00:01:59.532 --> 00:02:01.837
Milioni kumi---- hiyo ni idadi kubwa,

00:02:01.861 --> 00:02:03.858
lakini ni nambari lina suluhu,

00:02:03.882 --> 00:02:07.921
kwa sababu pia kuna dola bilioni 10

00:02:07.945 --> 00:02:11.313
ya madawa mazuri haijatumika

00:02:11.337 --> 00:02:12.733
yanayoharibika.

00:02:12.757 --> 00:02:15.389
Hii ni udhalimu kwa pande mbili:

00:02:15.413 --> 00:02:20.264
watu kutopata madawa
wanayohitaji kua hai na kustawi,

00:02:20.288 --> 00:02:25.917
na ni dawa hivi
vinatumwa kasha moto la madawa

00:02:25.941 --> 00:02:27.293
kuharibiwa.

00:02:27.317 --> 00:02:32.212
Huu uharibifu unapumbaza,
lakini pia unatoa fursa.